@startuml
' M5-partial / M6 fixture: parser support for the description-diagram
' family (component / actor / usecase / database / node) plus the
' inline shorthand `[Foo]` / `(Foo)` / `:Foo:`.
'
' v1 painter renders all these as class compartments (the kind keyword
' is emitted, but the painter dispatch falls back to the class shape).
' The full per-USymbol painter rollout is M5.

actor User
:GuestUser:
[WebApp]
component AuthService
(Login)
(Logout)

database "User DB" as UDB
node "App Server" as AS
cloud "External SSO" as SSO

User --> (Login)
User --> (Logout)
[WebApp] --> AuthService
AuthService --> UDB
AS --> SSO
@enduml
